    dc:description "Figure 1. Generated images for three query texts about dogs with different methods, including naive optimization with CLIP+GAN (top left of each panel), BigSleep [20] (top right of each panel), and FuseDream (the bottom row) with BigGAN-256 (left) and 512 (right)." ;
